	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b>Re: Nintendulator preference file location on Win7?</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The preferences are stored in the registry at HKEY_CURRENT_USER\SOFTWARE\Nintendulator (as is expected for well-behaved Windows applications), and savestates are stored in the APPDATA folder ([userprofiile]\Application Data on XP and earlier, [userprofiile]\AppData\Roaming on Vista and later).

		

		</td>
	</tr>
